{"tid":2030611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨立黨有能力於海外立即成立臨時政府，有意者請聯絡","createTime":"2020-05-23T00:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T02:00:39.000Z","uid":92301,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a0968c12e90c1298246357a05fd08f1712f343ac","tid":2030611,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:56:38.000Z","msg":"#請廣傳 #香港獨立黨 有能力於海外立即，係立即 #成立臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n成立臨時政府,係大家掙扎的最後機會<br />\n<br />\n有意者,請從速聯絡敝黨<br />\n<br />\n#pleasewidespread<br />\n<br />\n#hongkongindependenceparty can form a #provisionalgovernment in overseas right now.<br />\n<br />\nAnyone who intends to form the government together, please contact us #asap .<br />\n<br />\nMost likely it is our last chance to fight back. Thank you very much.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongIndependenceParty/posts/1301369276733985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongIndependenceParty%2Fposts%2F1301369276733985&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=7dd19371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongIndependenceParty/posts/1301369276733985</a>"},{"pid":"3d07bfd1f7d09660f0adb2d54ff4dd0347e81c65","tid":2030611,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:57:27.000Z","msg":"丟掉幻想, 大把和理非驚死 + 黑警戒嚴, 講大遊行果D只係一廂情願<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳[巴士人鏈]<br />\n限聚令豁免排隊, 黑警分唔到你係咪真排隊搭巴士<br />\n主力部隊集中去頭站, 只要頭站架架車滿載, 中途站上唔到車就可以排隊組人鏈<br />\n排到累去黃店抖吓, 差完電再排過<br />\n畫面夠靚, 岩哂和理非, 有機會上到國際頭版<br />\n<br />\n時間無多, 認同請代開post及分享給身邊黃絲朋友"},{"pid":"99c47f524756e1d712f938a54ae0c46b0f5c9a22","tid":2030611,"uid":20170,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T01:01:10.000Z","msg":"熱狗啲人嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/大公報續針對陳雲及其弟子-香港獨立黨成員大起底/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%A4%A